1. Introduction
Welcome to NPIXEL!
                                    This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and otherwise process personal information of a player, user, customer, subscriber, or online visitor (collectively, the
“User”
or
“you”
) of our mobile applications, games, websites, and other online services (collectively, the
“Services”
). NPIXEL may share your personal information with its affiliates and subsidiaries (collectively
“NPIXEL”
,
“we”
,
“us”
, or
“our”
) to the extent necessary to provide the Services to you.
                                    You confirm that you are above the age of majority, or if your country of residence states the minimum age for processing personal information otherwise such different age. We do not intend to collect any personal information from children. If you are children or the parent of any children using our Services, please refer to “Children” section below.
