3. Processing and Sharing Personal Information with Third Parties
We may transfer personal information we collect from you to the other region for the purposes set forth in this Privacy Policy.
We do not share or sell your personal information with any independent third parties without your consent. However, we collect and may share your personal information for the following purposes without obtaining your consent:
(a) to provide the Game and the Services to you, such as providing customer support, processing gameplay and game rendering data to provide game analytics to improve gameplay, and providing marketing and advertisements and monitoring the success of our marketing and advertising programs. All companies providing services for us, such as service providers in support of our Services, or providers of cloud services that process information identified in this policy on their servers, are prohibited from retaining, using, or disclosing your personal information for any purpose other than providing us with their services.
Trustee: Qroad Corporation
Purpose: customer service consulting service
Trustee: Xsolla Inc.
Purposet: enable alternative payment systems to be used for digital transactions
(b) to comply with any relevant laws or legal obligations or processes, including to comply with a court order or subpoena to provide information, to detect and protect against fraud or illegal activity, to prosecute those responsible for that activity, to enforce our legal rights and resolve disputes, and to ensure security.
(c) to sell, transfer, merge, consolidate or re-organize any parts of our business, or merge with, acquire or form a joint venture with, any other business, in which case we may disclose your data to any third party that acquires all or substantially all of us or our business, prospective buyer, or other relevant parties to such change. If we sell or transfer any of our assets, the information we hold about you may be sold as part of those assets and may be transferred.
If you have more questions about our business partners, please contact us at
