4. Opt Out Options
We may send local or push notifications to your mobile device to make you aware of game updates, promotional events, new game information, and other relevant messages regarding the Service. You can manage push notifications from the “options” or “settings” page within the game, or your device’s settings page for the relevant game.
If you wish to opt out of receiving commercial email messages, text messages, or interest-based ads from us, please contact us at .
Please note that we may still use or process your personal information pursuant to this Privacy Policy, such as sending official announcement related to the Services to you.
5. Children
We do not knowingly collect or store any personally identifiable information from children under the age of 13 (or if your country of residence states the minimum age for processing personal information otherwise such different age). If any parents believe that we have unintentionally collected your child’s personal information, we will promptly delete the information upon your request. In this case, please send a request to us at .
We have listed the relevant minimum age in the table below for Users located in certain regions. PLEASE NOTE that it is your responsibility to refer to the laws in your country of residence to ensure you are above the relevant legal minimum age. We do not make any representation or warranty as to accuracy and completeness of the information below.
