12. Modification
This Privacy Policy may change from time to time, so please check back periodically to ensure that you are aware of any changes. If we make a material change to this Privacy Policy, we will notify you by posting the change within our Services or in this Privacy Policy, and, if necessary, give you additional choices regarding such change prior to the change becoming effective.
                                    Your continued use of the NPIXEL Services will signify your acceptance of these changes.